data.description: Stunning home in sought-after Grassfield school district, nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac. The living room features charming built-ins, cathedral ceilings, and a cozy ceiling nook. With an airy, open floor plan flooded with natural light, this home is perfect for entertaining. Upgrades include a new roof and wrapped exterior in 2014. The kitchen is a chef's dream with soft close drawers, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a breakfast bar, and ample storage. Additionally, the mud room/utility room on the 1st floor, chair rail molding, and wainscoting in the kitchen and dining room. The master bedroom boasts his and her closets, the master bath features dual sinks, abundant storage, and a spacious walk-in shower with travertine tile. The bonus room offers versatility as a bedroom, man cave, or office. Not to forget the new HVAC system, kitchen appliances, white vinyl fence, and ceiling fans! Relax in the expansive, shaded fenced-in backyard with your loved ones.
